Board and advisory work[edit]
Sarandos is a member of many boards.[14]

Academy of Television Arts & Sciences, Executive Committee Appointee (2015), Member[41]
Digital Entertainment Group, Retail Advisory Board[citation needed]
Exploring The Arts, Board of Trustees[42]
International Documentary Association, Trustee[43]
