Insider Activity


Individual




Theodore A. Sarandos



Mr. Theodore A. Sarandos is Chief Content Officer at Netflix, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at International Documentary Association, Exploring the Arts, Inc., American Cinematheque, and American Film Institute, Inc.
Mr. Sarandos was previously employed as Vice President-Product & Merchandising by Video City, Inc. He also served on the board at Video Software Dealers Association.



